INSERT INTO `joshe_virtuemart_products_en_gb` VALUES
(2, 'The Raspberry Pi Zero is half the size of a Model A+, with twice the utility. ', '<p><br />A tiny Raspberry Pi that’s affordable enough for any project! Raspberry Pi Zero runs Raspbian and all your favorite applications, including Scratch, Minecraft, and Sonic Pi. 40% faster than Raspberry Pi 1.</p>', 'Raspberry Pi Zero', '', '', '', 'raspberry-pi-zero'),
(3, '', '<p>Built on the latest Broadcom 2837 ARMv8 64 bit processor the Raspberry Pi 3 Model B is faster and more powerful than its predecessors. It has improved power management to support more powerful external USB devices and now comes with built-in wireless and Bluetooth connectivity. To take full advantage of the improved power management on the Raspberry Pi 3 and provide support for even more powerful devices on the USB ports, a 2.5A adapter is required. </p>', 'Raspberry Pi 3 Model B ', '', '', '', 'raspberry-pi-3-model-b'),
(4, '', '<p>The Raspberry Pi Sense HAT Shield can be used for the Raspberry Pi A +, B +, 2 &amp; 3. With the aid of the Raspberry Pi Sense HAT module, you are able to use a wide range of applications, experiments and even games, thanks to the various sensors, such as acceleration sensor, 3D gyroscope and magnetometer (compass), air pressure sensor, humidity sensor and temperature sensor. The LED array on the shield allows direct display of the various sensor data, e.g. The direction of the geomagnetic north. But also games like Tetris, Pong or Snake can be played using the joystick as long as they have been integrated. In addition, the joystick of the Sensor HAT board can also be used to interact directly with programs on the Raspberry Pi.</p>', 'Raspberry Pi Sense HAT', '', '', '', 'raspberry-pi-sense-hat'),
(5, '', '<p>This Li-ion 18650 Battery mosltly used in battery bank and this battery is good solution for replacements. </p>\r\n<p>Top type can be change. (Flat or Top)</p>', 'Li-ion 18650 Rechargeable Battery', '', '', '', 'li-ion-18650-rechargeable-battery'),
(6, '', '<p>This battery applies for torches and much more new electronic devices. This Battery comes with battery top and this not suitable for topless 18650 battery replacement</p>', 'Rechargeable Battery 3800mAh ', '', '', '', 'rechargeable-battery-3800mah'),
(7, '', '<p>Large Hot Glue Gun GG-5 is a very useful tool for joining plastic materials and even more substantial materials can be fixed together with it.</p>', 'Large Hot Glue Gun', '', '', '', 'large-hot-glue-gun'),
(8, '', '<p>It is a professional and cheap Mini Drill Set for cutting, engraving, milling, grinding, drawing, cutting, grinding, drilling and removal. It is designed for applications of porcelain, plastic, wood, etc. </p>', 'Mini Drill Set', '', '', '', 'mini-drill-set'),
(9, '', '<p>The SRf05 ultrasonic range sensor detects objects in it,s path and can be used to calculate the range to the object. It is sensitive enough to detect any object around 3 cm to 3 m range.</p>', 'Ultrasonic Sensor HY-SRF05', '', '', '', 'ultrasonic-sensor-hy-srf05'),
(10, '', '<p>This Automatic water tank level controller Using a relay and the input of two sensors (max-limit and min-limit sensors), this module is capable of switching devices on and off accordingly. It is ideal for applications where one needs to control the liquid level of a tank. In such application, whenever the liquid level is at minimum, the min-limit sensor should trigger the relay powering the pump on and filling the tank with the liquid. Once the liquid level has reached the maximum level, the max-limit should trigger the module and make the relay switch the pump off and so on.</p>', 'Automatic Water Level Controller XH-M203 with 2 Sensors', '', '', '', 'automatic-water-level-controller-xh-m203-with-2-sensors'),
(11, '', '<p>GP2Y0A02YK0F is a distance measuring sensor unit, composed of an integrated combination of PSD (position sensitive detector) , IRED (infrared emitting diode) and signal processing circuit. The variety of the reflectivity of the object, the environmental temperature and the operating duration are not influenced easily to the distance detection because of adopting the triangulation method. This device outputs the voltage corresponding to the detection distance. So this sensor can also be used as a proximity sensor.</p>', 'SHARP Distance Sensor 2Y0A02', '', '', '', 'sharp-distance-sensor-2y0a02'),
(12, '', '<p>The Arduino Stater Kit walks you through the basics of using the Arduino in a hands-on way. You''ll learn through building several creative projects. The kit includes a selection of the most common and useful electronic components. Starting the basics of electronics, to more complex projects, the kit will help you control the physical world with sensor and actuators. </p>', 'Arduino Starter Kit Advance', '', '', '', 'arduino-starter-kit-advance'),
(13, '', '<p>Arduino/Genuino Uno is a microcontroller board based on the ATmega328P. It has 14 digital input/output pins (of which 6 can be used as PWM outputs), 6 analog inputs, a 16 MHz quartz crystal, a USB connection, a power jack, an ICSP header and a reset button. It contains everything needed to support the microcontroller; simply connect it to a computer with a USB cable or power it with a AC-to-DC adapter or battery to get started.. You can tinker with your UNO without worring too much about doing something wrong, worst case scenario you can replace the chip for a few dollars and start over again.</p>', 'Arduino Uno Compatible R3', '', '', '', 'arduino-uno-compatible-r3'),
(14, '', '<p>The Arduino Leonardo is a microcontroller board based on the ATmega32u4. It has 20 digital input/output pins (of which 7 can be used as PWM outputs and 12 as analog inputs), a 16 MHz crystal oscillator, a micro USB connection, a power jack, an ICSP header, and a reset button. It contains everything needed to support the microcontroller; simply connect it to a computer with a USB cable or power it with a AC-to-DC adapter or battery to get started.</p>', 'Arduino Leonardo Compatible', '', '', '', 'arduino-leonardo-compatible'),
(15, '', '<p>The Mega 2560 is a microcontroller board based on the Atmega2560. It has 54 digital input/output pins (of which 15 can be used as PWM outputs), 16 analog inputs, 4 UARTs (hardware serial ports), a 16 MHz crystal oscillator, a USB connection, a power jack, an ICSP header, and a reset button. It contains everything needed to support the microcontroller; simply connect it to a computer with a USB cable or power it with a AC-to-DC adapter or battery to get started. The Mega 2560 board is compatible with most shields designed for the Uno and the former boards Duemilanove or Diecimila.</p>', 'Arduino Mega 2560 Compatible', '', '', '', 'arduino-mega-2560-compatible');

